# .github/workflows — CI pipelines
#
# Wired in M0.5 (per plan §17 and v1.2 §22.15 L1 reordering):
#   ci.yml             — lint (ruff/eslint) + typecheck (mypy/tsc) + tests + e2e
#   deploy-staging.yml — Fly + Vercel deploys on merge to staging
#   deploy-prod.yml    — same to prod, with manual approval gate
